WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.629
I was praying and the Lord showed me,

00:00:02.629 --> 00:00:02.639
saying,

00:00:02.639 --> 00:00:05.829
'I need you to pray for Italy.'I

00:00:05.829 --> 00:00:05.839
asked,

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:07.349
'What's going on with Italy,

00:00:07.349 --> 00:00:07.359
Lord?'He

00:00:07.359 --> 00:00:09.390
showed me—I had

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:11.190
that open vision

00:00:11.190 --> 00:00:11.200
again—a

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:14.430
massive volcano that's

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:17.510
about to happen. I saw a coastline

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:19.990
on the water where there's a

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.109
massive volcano. He told me

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:26.189
this is going to happen and

00:00:26.199 --> 00:00:28.390
there will be signs right before

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:31.109
a massive explosion. I saw this

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:35.069
thing explode huge, and He kept having me

00:00:35.069 --> 00:00:35.079
pray

00:00:35.079 --> 00:00:38.150
over the ocean. There's

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:40.790
something about the water

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.430
around Italy. I believe the volcano was right

00:00:46.150 --> 00:00:46.160
there,

00:00:47.440 --> 00:00:50.189
because Pompeii is right here

00:00:50.189 --> 00:00:50.199
and

00:00:50.199 --> 00:00:52.389
there's a massive volcano up here.

00:00:52.389 --> 00:00:52.399
When

00:00:52.399 --> 00:00:54.110
I was looking

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:56.150
over in the spirit

00:00:56.150 --> 00:00:56.160
realm,

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:57.950
I thought it was in this area, but

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:00.830
I believe it's probably further out.

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:03.069
I started looking at where the

00:01:03.079 --> 00:01:06.149
massive volcanoes in the water are in

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:08.310
Italy. If you zoom out, I'll show

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:11.710
you;

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:14.350
one of the largest is way

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:17.830
down here. Whenever I saw

00:01:17.830 --> 00:01:17.840
this

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:20.469
massive volcano going off out of the

00:01:20.479 --> 00:01:23.390
water, it caused a massive tsunami

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:26.510
wave. From the

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:28.310
earthquake and this massive volcano, it

00:01:28.310 --> 00:01:28.320
was

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:30.830
like a humongous

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:33.310
nuclear bomb went

00:01:33.310 --> 00:01:33.320
off—it

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:34.870
went up out of the water and caused a

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:37.389
massive wave. The water rushed all

00:01:37.399 --> 00:01:39.710
over this area,

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:42.429
causing

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:45.190
a lot of devastation.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:49.830
The Lord is showing me it came

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:52.270
up out of the water and caused

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:54.389
all the air traffic around that area to

00:01:54.389 --> 00:01:54.399
be

00:01:54.399 --> 00:01:56.350
completely shut down. The Lord showed me

00:01:56.360 --> 00:01:58.350
it would cost hundreds of

00:01:58.360 --> 00:02:00.230
thousands of deaths. There

00:02:00.230 --> 00:02:00.240
will

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:04.190
be signs, maybe even on the news

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:08.029
in Italy, about rumblings

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:10.550
around that area, earthquakes,

00:02:10.550 --> 00:02:10.560
or

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:13.430
tremors to

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:13.440
warn

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:16.790
that something big is going to happen. Do

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:20.070
not ignore this; it is

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:23.790
very serious.

00:02:26.519 --> 00:02:28.509
If you start having a lot of tremors and

00:02:28.519 --> 00:02:31.030
you start seeing smoke,

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:34.830
take heed.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:37.589
Be forewarned; I'm trying to

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:39.509
tell you. I was just

00:02:39.519 --> 00:02:40.589
praying in the spirit,

00:02:40.599 --> 00:02:42.949
worshiping, and all of a sudden I was

00:02:42.959 --> 00:02:46.190
shot up. I was looking

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:50.790
over Italy, and it

00:02:50.790 --> 00:02:50.800
looked

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:51.949
so

00:02:51.959 --> 00:02:56.350
small because I was so high

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.790
up.

00:02:57.800 --> 00:03:00.229
I was looking

00:03:00.239 --> 00:03:04.229
down and all of a sudden I could see

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:07.710
a

00:03:07.720 --> 00:03:11.869
black blanket over the water.

00:03:11.869 --> 00:03:11.879
It was a

00:03:11.879 --> 00:03:14.869
very thick cloud,

00:03:14.879 --> 00:03:18.309
as

00:03:18.319 --> 00:03:23.470
black as molasses,

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:27.470
very dark.

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:33.949
I could see the

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:37.229
black clouds going through all the

00:03:37.239 --> 00:03:42.630
houses like a smog.

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:49.509
I could see the rooftops

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:51.830
of the homes

00:03:51.830 --> 00:03:51.840
and

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:54.750
the lights on

00:03:54.760 --> 00:03:55.670
inside.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:59.869
The Lord pointed my attention

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:04.869
to a massive circle, a

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:07.910
humongous portal

00:04:07.910 --> 00:04:07.920
over

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:10.670
Italy

00:04:10.670 --> 00:04:10.680
near

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:13.750
where the

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:16.069
volcano was

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:18.469
by

00:04:18.469 --> 00:04:18.479
Pompeii.

00:04:18.479 --> 00:04:22.790
Angels were coming out

00:04:22.790 --> 00:04:22.800
of

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:24.590
this massive portal.

00:04:32.520 --> 00:04:34.990
It was alive, swirling

00:04:34.990 --> 00:04:35.000
with

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:37.790
clouds,

00:04:37.790 --> 00:04:37.800
and

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:39.990
opening up.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.189
All of a

00:04:42.199 --> 00:04:44.469
sudden, thousands of angels started coming out

00:04:44.479 --> 00:04:46.469
of this massive

00:04:46.479 --> 00:04:50.270
portal

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:53.390
like

00:04:56.469 --> 00:04:56.479
soldiers,

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:02.710
lined up

00:05:02.710 --> 00:05:02.720
and

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:05.950
descending.

00:05:05.950 --> 00:05:05.960
Through

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:08.350
the

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:10.950
portal,

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:26.029
clouds were

00:05:26.039 --> 00:05:29.189
coming out—humongous,

00:05:29.189 --> 00:05:29.199
beautiful

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:31.510
pink,

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:34.270
fluffy, blue,

00:05:34.280 --> 00:05:36.870
and

00:05:39.990 --> 00:05:40.000
purple.

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:45.390
I believe it was Heaven.

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:47.830
These angels were

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:49.830
descending

00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:52.510
onto the Earth.

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:55.110
When they reached

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:55.120
the

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:59.430
atmosphere,

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:02.029
they started

00:06:02.039 --> 00:06:05.110
to spread out like ants,

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:06.710
moving

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:09.070
at

00:06:09.080 --> 00:06:12.510
the

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:14.990
speed

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:16.710
of

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.270
light

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:19.629
on a mission.

00:06:22.919 --> 00:06:26.309
They all had beautiful

00:06:26.319 --> 00:06:28.550
robes and gowns on. It

00:06:28.550 --> 00:06:28.560
was

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:30.230
amazing.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:33.150
I'm just

00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:35.189
sitting here in this chair praying in

00:06:35.199 --> 00:06:36.870
the spirit, soaking it all

00:06:39.830 --> 00:06:39.840
in.

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:44.390
I

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:47.440
asked

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:53.270
the

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:57.589
Lord what

00:06:57.599 --> 00:06:59.909
that black smog was, and He showed me there is

00:07:07.039 --> 00:07:08.909
a

00:07:08.919 --> 00:07:11.189
lot of trafficking and corruption in Italy.

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:30.990
Those angels were

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:34.390
going to homes

00:07:34.400 --> 00:07:36.230
and

00:07:36.230 --> 00:07:36.240
waving

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:39.270
their

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.430
hands,

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:44.270
telling people to

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:46.629
leave, warning

00:07:56.110 --> 00:07:56.120
them.

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:07.270
You

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:10.110
could sense an urgency on their

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:12.510
faces.

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:31.430
All of a sudden, the

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:34.829
angels stopped.

00:08:37.479 --> 00:08:39.469
I could feel the intercessory

00:08:39.479 --> 00:08:42.750
prayers from the saints

00:08:42.760 --> 00:08:45.150
interceding for

00:08:45.160 --> 00:08:46.910
Italy in the spirit.

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:50.230
You could

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:52.870
feel the blanket of prayer

00:08:52.880 --> 00:08:55.310
above

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:58.269
the atmosphere.

00:09:09.160 --> 00:09:13.630
All of a sudden, all the angels froze

00:09:13.630 --> 00:09:13.640
and

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:16.470
turned

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:19.310
their bodies to look back up

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:24.389
to the massive swirling light

00:09:24.389 --> 00:09:24.399
of

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:27.350
the portal. They

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:38.990
started

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.230
shooting back up into that

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:42.710
portal.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:47.870
Then the Lord took me

00:09:47.870 --> 00:09:47.880
to

00:09:47.880 --> 00:09:50.670
another part of the vision. He

00:09:50.680 --> 00:09:54.430
said, 'I want you to focus on the canary.'What is the

00:09:54.430 --> 00:09:54.440
meaning of a

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:57.829
canary in

00:09:57.829 --> 00:09:57.839
a

00:09:57.839 --> 00:10:01.190
coal

00:10:01.190 --> 00:10:01.200
mine?

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:04.790
Study this out. I saw a yellow canary

00:10:04.800 --> 00:10:08.509
in a cage. There was

00:10:08.519 --> 00:10:12.110
gas

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:19.030
like a smog coming

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:22.069
up out of the ground. The canary

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:25.389
was swinging in its cage in the spirit realm. It was chirping, but then I looked down at the mist coming up

00:10:25.389 --> 00:10:25.399
out of the ground. When I looked back up, the canary was at the bottom of the

00:10:25.399 --> 00:10:27.910
cage,

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:34.550
lifeless.

00:10:39.190 --> 00:10:39.200
This

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:50.389
gas coming up out of

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:52.949
the ground

00:11:01.710 --> 00:11:01.720
in

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:16.949
Italy—I

00:11:25.639 --> 00:11:29.069
don't know if it was from

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:31.710
the volcano,

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.870
but I saw

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.949
hundreds of thousands of people go home.

00:11:38.959 --> 00:11:41.629
A massive wave was coming. The

00:11:41.639 --> 00:11:44.350
Lord said to pay attention to the water. I

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:46.949
saw earthquakes in

00:11:57.639 --> 00:11:59.710
the water, and He kept pointing me to

00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:01.030
that in the spirit realm. In my spirit

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:02.829
eyes, I could see

00:12:02.829 --> 00:12:02.839
the

00:12:02.839 --> 00:12:03.990
water

00:12:03.990 --> 00:12:04.000
in

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:06.949
the

00:12:06.949 --> 00:12:06.959
gulf

00:12:06.959 --> 00:12:09.030
area, the gulf right

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:13.230
there by

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:17.870
Pompeii.

00:12:21.199 --> 00:12:24.790
For three weeks now, the Lord has

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:28.110
spoken to me about the electric grid

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:31.870
in America, telling me to pray over the

00:12:31.880 --> 00:12:35.189
electric grid. This is serious. I saw

00:12:35.199 --> 00:12:37.750
a cyberattack or a false

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:40.350
flag.

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:54.550
Power went out in New York and

00:12:54.560 --> 00:12:57.550
major cities.

00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:05.550
He

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:07.389
warned me that I need to pray about

00:13:07.399 --> 00:13:10.670
this more intently

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:12.910
because of what is being planned.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:20.269
I saw that when the electric grid went

00:13:20.279 --> 00:13:22.430
down, it had the

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:25.350
opportunity to be down for over

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.670
three weeks. I saw a calendar

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:31.470
with

00:13:31.480 --> 00:13:34.150
the days going by.

00:13:59.399 --> 00:14:01.710
He showed me a year ago to

00:14:01.710 --> 00:14:01.720
invest in

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:03.590
a generator

00:14:03.590 --> 00:14:03.600
with

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:06.829
three fuel types—propane, gas, and

00:14:06.839 --> 00:14:10.269
natural

00:14:10.279 --> 00:14:12.350
gas—and

00:14:12.360 --> 00:14:15.389
solar

00:14:15.399 --> 00:14:18.790
power.

00:14:30.199 --> 00:14:32.269
I don't want to preach fear,

00:14:35.639 --> 00:14:38.670
but I get these intense

00:14:38.670 --> 00:14:38.680
warnings

00:14:38.680 --> 00:14:40.670
from the Spirit of God.

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:47.710
For

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:52.310
instance, I was praying over an ice

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:55.550
storm once and He told me

00:14:55.560 --> 00:14:58.230
about Texas being without power. I kept

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:00.790
seeing no

00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:03.470
heat and a poisoning of

00:15:03.480 --> 00:15:05.150
the water.

00:15:05.160 --> 00:15:08.110
About three years

00:15:08.110 --> 00:15:08.120
ago,

00:15:08.120 --> 00:15:11.710
a

00:15:11.720 --> 00:15:15.269
major arctic front

00:15:17.160 --> 00:15:19.590
made

00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:22.389
everything really cold in

00:15:22.399 --> 00:15:26.110
Texas.

00:15:29.319 --> 00:15:31.189
The

00:15:33.639 --> 00:15:35.670
grid shut down,

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:38.990
pipes

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:42.350
burst,

00:15:42.360 --> 00:15:44.590
and

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:47.269
they put

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:50.470
out a warning not to drink the

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:52.670
water because it had

00:15:52.680 --> 00:15:54.870
E.

00:15:57.629 --> 00:15:57.639
coli.

00:16:00.959 --> 00:16:03.990
Before that happened, the Lord warned me

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:06.990
to tell friends in Texas

00:16:06.990 --> 00:16:07.000
they

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:09.910
needed

00:16:09.920 --> 00:16:14.949
cases of water.

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:19.309
I

00:16:21.399 --> 00:16:22.949
bought water too

00:16:22.959 --> 00:16:24.389
because what I was seeing in the spirit

00:16:24.399 --> 00:16:26.150
was very alarming.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.749
Even

00:16:31.759 --> 00:16:35.509
if

00:16:35.519 --> 00:16:36.749
it

00:16:36.759 --> 00:16:38.870
doesn't

00:16:38.880 --> 00:16:41.590
always affect

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:44.509
everybody,

00:16:49.509 --> 00:16:49.519
I

00:16:54.000 --> 00:16:55.269
want to

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:05.949
be

00:17:05.949 --> 00:17:05.959
quick

00:17:08.309 --> 00:17:08.319
to

00:17:08.319 --> 00:17:10.630
obey.

00:17:10.640 --> 00:17:13.390
I saw New York, a major

00:17:13.400 --> 00:17:15.949
city

00:17:15.959 --> 00:17:18.309
with

00:17:18.319 --> 00:17:21.069
big buildings.

00:17:21.079 --> 00:17:23.909
Pray about

00:17:23.919 --> 00:17:26.470
the power grid with me. I don't

00:17:26.470 --> 00:17:26.480
want to

00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:29.630
be a

00:17:29.630 --> 00:17:29.640
Debbie Downer and

00:17:29.640 --> 00:17:31.909
coming on

00:17:31.909 --> 00:17:31.919
here and

00:17:31.919 --> 00:17:34.830
going

00:17:45.110 --> 00:17:45.120
wacky

00:17:57.280 --> 00:17:59.630
all the

00:18:01.270 --> 00:18:01.280
time,

00:18:02.919 --> 00:18:04.950
but

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:44.430
these

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:46.390
are the

00:18:46.400 --> 00:18:48.470
three things:

00:18:48.480 --> 00:18:49.990
the canary,

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:53.070
Italy, and

00:18:53.080 --> 00:18:55.909
the electric grid.

00:19:06.919 --> 00:19:08.070
Let's

00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:10.350
pray.

00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:21.350
Father, I thank You.

00:19:21.360 --> 00:19:24.710
We lift up

00:19:24.720 --> 00:19:28.230
Italy, the volcano, and the

00:19:28.240 --> 00:19:30.350
earthquakes.

00:19:30.360 --> 00:19:33.430
You warned us that

00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:36.510
perilous times would come.

00:20:09.919 --> 00:20:13.110
Shake us and show us

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:14.750
what we're supposed to do for our

00:20:14.760 --> 00:20:17.029
families so we hear You before

00:20:17.039 --> 00:20:19.390
danger comes.

00:20:21.830 --> 00:20:21.840
Let

00:20:24.320 --> 00:20:27.710
us

